items.summary: Ensure frontend/vite.config.ts or frontend/vite.config.js exists with proper configuration for React, TypeScript support, and Internet Computer environment variables

Create complete frontend/package.json with all required dependencies including React, TypeScript, Vite, TanStack Router, TanStack Query, @dfinity/agent, @dfinity/auth-client, @dfinity/candid, @dfinity/principal, Tailwind CSS, and all other necessary packages for the React + Internet Computer application
Create frontend/package-lock.json with resolved dependency tree matching the package.json configuration to enable proper npm install execution
